casebody.data:
No. 36,

Orig.

Texas v. Louisiana. [For earlier orders herein, see, e. g., 413 U. S. 918.]

Application for temporary restraining order, preliminary injunction, and other relief referred to Special Master. Report of Special Master on Louisiana’s motion to enlarge reference to Special Master to include establishment of Louisiana’s lateral boundary with Texas in the Gulf of Mexico, including briefing schedule contained therein, received and ordered filed and adopted.
